        protected java.util.Set<java.lang.Integer> getMethodCallArities(java.util.List<java.util.List<IToken>> parameterTokens)
        Returns a set of possible method call arities for the given parameter tokens. This is necessary to represent the different possible arities for extension methods. The default implementation returns a set that contains the size of the given parameter tokens list.
